'''Boribos Prefecture''' was an area of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It bordered [[Hirkenglade Prefecture]] and [[CoCo Town/Legends|CoCo Town]], and was connected to them by [[Skyroute D25D]].<ref name="HoloNet 46">{{HoloNetNewsWeb|46|news/1337_3.html|Skyroute D25D Detoured}}</ref> The [[Duros Cultural Center]] was located here.<ref name="Republic HoloNet News Core Edition 15:3:02">{{InsiderCite|75|Republic HoloNet News Core Edition 15:3:02}}</ref>

